quran[54]{c,v,t}:
  44,17,Nummah keenik (Makki koros kinnuk) duma firqawnaa kee firqawni mara niqiyyireeh massakaxxa-le farmoyti keenih yemeete (Nabii Muusa kinnuk)
  44,18,Nabii Muusa Yallih naqoosa yol tabisa diggah anu siinih amaanat-le farmoyta kinniyok keenik iyye
  44,19,"Kaadu Yallal makaxxa-mariinitina, diggaluk anu baxxaqqa-le sumaq siinih baaheyyo kay farmoyta kinniyoomuh"
  44,20,Kaadu anu diggaluk yi-Rabbiiy sin- Rabbi kinni Rabbi eleelita xeetit yoo qiddaanamak
  44,21,"Kaadu yoo nummayse wayteenik, toysa anay yoo ixxicaay, adá yoo abtaanamak yok exxeera"
  44,22,"Tokkel Nabii Muusa isi Rabbih seeceh firqawnaa kee firqawni mara kaa dirabbosse waqdi, diggah a-mari uma maray Yallal koroosite axcuk"
  44,23,"Toysa Muusaw yi-naqoosak koo nummayse mara barat kuulus, diggah firqawnaa kee firqawni mari sin katayeloonuk kaak iyye Yalli"
  44,24,"Kaadu bad baxsimit edde cab saayah anuk, diggah usun macaxuy badat yanxuqsumuwaa kinnoonuk kaak iyye Yalli"
  44,25,Makinam cabeeniih firqawnaa kee firqawni mari busaatin kee daroorik badat finqiteeniik lakal
  44,26,Kaadu usun buqreeraa kee meqé aroocak makinam cabeeniih
  44,27,Kaadu niqmatittey ruffu edde axcuk sugeenik makinam caben
  44,28,"Tonnaah, aki-mara tet (niqmatitte kinnuk) nagarsisne (israa-iil xaylo kinnuk)"
  44,29,"Tokkel qaran kee baaxó keenih (firqawnaa kee firqawni mara kinnuk) maweeqinnaay, digaalák mohlá kah yeceen mara makkon"
  44,30,Yalli nummah xiibiteh israa-iil xaylo rammissah tan digaalák ken naggoyseemil
  44,31,Yalli Firqawni keenit abak suge digaalák ken cateh. Diggaluk usuk (firqawna kinnuk) jabbiiriy nacrur sinniy kaxxa-mariinoh caddok taturleelat yanik suge
  44,32,Yalli nummah xiibiteh israa-iil xaylo ken waktih marak aaxaguk ken doorre axcuk
  44,33,Kaadu keenih neceeh astootik baxxaqqa- le aqayyaare edde tanim Nabii Muusâ gabal
  44,34,Diggaluk nabiyow a-mari (Makki koros kinnuk) iyyah
  44,35,"Rabi mayan addunyal abne naharsi raba akke waytek, kaadu nanu rabneek lakal ugsuma mara hinnino qhiyaamah ayró"
  44,36,"Toysa Mucammadow koo kee kol yeemene mara ni-abbobtiy rabte baahay, ittaanamal numma-le mara tekkeenik iyyan"
  44,37,Caylah usun (Makki koros kinnuk) yayseeni innaa? hinnay Tubbaq maraa kee keenik naharat suge mari yaysee? ken finqisnehik diggah usun umá marah sugeenimih sabbatah
  44,38,"Qaranwaa kee baaxooy, ken nammayih fanal tanim digirih ma- gininnino iyye Yalli"
  44,39,"Ken nammay (qaranwaa kee baaxó kinnuk) ma-gininnino cakkil ken ginnem akke waytek, kinnih immay keenik (koros kinnuk) maggo mari woh mayaaxiga"
  44,40,Diggah meklah ayró (Qhiyaamah ayró kinnuk) inkih keenik xagni ayró
  44,41,"Woh xayni-xaynah tu-xiqewaah, kataysa-kataysah tu-xiqewaa ayroóy, usun ken cattam malon"
  44,42,"Yalli kah racmate num akke waytek (moomintu kinnuk), diggaluk yalli mayso-li, xuwaw-li"
  44,43,Diggah Zaqhqhuum deqsitta caxáy Jahannamak addak tawqe
  44,44,Tet mexexi kaxxa-dambi-li (korosta kinnuk) maaqó
  44,45,Eelisen (diyaayisen) nacaasih innah ken (koros kinnuk) bagul faca (goomaaxa)
  44,46,Niqna kak caddok taturte leeh faciyyih innah faca ken bagul
  44,47,"A-kaxxa dambiliy umeynah yani ibbixaay, hirriigisak kaa beya jaciim deqsitta girák gudê fan, iyyan malaykak"
  44,48,Tohuk wadir amok kaal caxa niqná kak caddok taturte leeh digaalá
  44,49,"Tammos tama digaalá, diggaluk atu mayso-le konnaba-li kinnitok kaak iyyan anqasah"
  44,50,"Diggaluk tamah agay-waaga kak luk sugten digaalák, tammoysa tet asaaku keenik iyyan"
  44,51,Diggaluk Yallak meesita mari saayah (amaanah) yan aracal yanin
  44,52,Jannootaa kee daroorih addal yanin
  44,53,Sarak ‘Sundus’ deqsita cariiriy xabcinii kee ‘Istabraqh’ deqsita cariiriy gibdi saritan sittâ fan afkanuk
  44,54,Tonnaah kaadu Jannatti agabuy ‘curral-qeyni’ deqsita keenih rihmisne
  44,55,Kay addal caxâ mixuk kulli qaynat esseritan keenik yaggiriqqeeh yanbaxeemih meesik amaanah anuk (saayah anuk)
  44,56,Jannat addal raba ma-tammoysan (Yallak meesitta moominiin kinnuk) naharsi rabay addunyal tammoyseeni akke waytek. Kaadu Yalli Jaciim deqsitta giráh digaalák ken catah
  44,57,"Woo mattaccoo ku-Rabbi-le qaxak keenih kaxxa muxxo kinni, woo niqmat usuk kaxxa affaafa"
  44,58,"Toysa cagalah nabiyow ku- afay Qarab-af kinnit kaa (Qhuraan kinnuk) xabbacosne usun (koros kinnuk) kassitaah, yaamineeh umaanek waasima mara yakkeenî gidah"
  44,59,"Toysa nabiyow ken finqa qambal, diggah usun ku-finqa qambaala mara kinnoonuk"
  45,1,Caa-Miim- (edde faxem Yalli yaaxige)
  45,2,A Qhuraanih oobiyyi Yallay mayso-ley naggaarah yanih kabuk yekke
  45,3,"Diggah qaranwaa kee baaxô ginooy, ken nammayih addal ginoonak taniimit yeemene marah Yallih nabnaa kee dudda tascasse astooti tan"
  45,4,Kaadu sinaamey Yalli siinit abe ginoo kee mutuccu ittaamat abeh yan ginoo kee fixiixisiyyat yaamineeh yasmite marah Yallaa kee Yallih diinih nabna tascasse astooti tan
  45,5,Kaadu bar kee laqó sittal abtah tan ciggiiliyyaa kee Yalli qaraanak oobiseh yaniimit roobuk baaxó kaat yaynuwwuh is qabaarah rabteeh kafteek lakal kaadu kulli kabuk caacayat abah yan Koran- korsiyyat astooti tan kas-le maray kas-kassoowah
  45,6,"Tamah Yallih astootiy nummah kol nakriyeeh koh warisna nabiyow, tokkel Yallaa kee Yallih yaabaay kay astootik lakal elle yaamineenim mayaabaay? Wohul aamine weenik"
  45,7,Ummaan kaxxa dirablih maggo dambilih finqi yan
  45,8,"Yallih kitaabih aayoota kaal ankirriyimah yaabbeeh, tohuk lakat kaxxa-mariinitak koroosannul amo-ayxeeruk raaqa tet aabbewaah innah, toysa nabiyow Jahannam giráh digaaláy kaa qansarissal kaa ayti-kumus"
  45,9,Kaadu ama maggo dambi-li Ni- qhuraanih aayootak-tu yeexege waqdi anqasah tet haysite. Too mari ken rammissa digaalá- lon qhiyaamah ayró Qhuraanal anqaseenimih sabbatah
  45,10,"Keenik (Qhuraanal anqassa koros kinnuk) foocal jahannam yaniih, maaluu kee xaylok yeddereenim tu-keenih maxiqta kaadu Yallak kalah aqbaduk sugen yallitte Yallih digaalák keenih xiqtam maliiy, usun kaxxa digaalá-lon"
  45,11,"Nabiyow ama kol oobisne Qhuraan makot gexok tirtó kinni. sinni Rabbih aayootal koroositeeh, yengedde mari qansaru-le digaaláy lafet-le-lon qhiyaamah ayró"